						<h5>Key Manager - Contact Centre, Max Bupa</h5>
						<p>“I’ve been with Max Bupa since 2011. Every day there is something new to learn or some challenge that makes things interesting and exciting. The company is constantly growing and moving forward and is driven by some extremely experienced senior managers and backed up by some of the best in the industry. Although the culture is relaxed and friendly, we are always looking to improve and streamline our processes to make our products and services the best out there.”</p>
