				<div class="testimonial-div">
					<div class="testimonial-content">
						<h4>Dr. Dhirja Sharma</h4>
						<h5> Vice President, Medical Quality and Performance Improvement, Max Healthcare </h5>
						<p>“Max Healthcare pioneered the concept of Medical and service excellence in Healthcare delivery in our country. Over the years, an unwavering focus on the same has not only made working here as a physician a pleasure, but also an experience past compare.”</p>
					</div>
					<img src="/static/images/testimonial-img2.jpg"/>
				</div>
