					<img src="/static/images/testimonial-img3.jpg"/>
					<div class="testimonial-content">
						<h4>Ishan Bummi</h4>
						<h5> Chief Manager – Renewals, Max Bupa</h5>
						<p>“Max Bupa has given me an opportunity to build on my past experience and knowledge. The organization has helped me in improving my skills and hence enabling me to work towards company’s vision of helping the customers to live healthier and successful lives. It has been a pleasure and a great learning experience working with the organization.”</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="testimonial-div">
					<div class="testimonial-content">
						<h4>Mohan Menon</h4>
						<h5>General Manager - Brand & Marketing Communications, Max Healthcare</h5>
						<p>“Working at Max Healthcare is more than just a job; it’s about passion and working to make a difference in someone’s life. It is this vision that has made my journey at Max very special. When I joined Max almost 3 years ago, I didn’t know that this stint would be so rewarding, both personally and professionally. While I have learnt at every step professionally and worked with some of the best people, it is my personal learning that makes this journey so memorable. I am inspired by our dedication to achieve excellence, not just as a corporate value but in everything we do. I feel a sense of fulfilment when I see my communication making a difference in the life of a patient, explaining things easily to them, making hospitals a little less scary and at the same time making this environment even more exciting & friendly for my colleagues.”</p>
					</div>
					<img src="/static/images/testimonial-img4.jpg"/>
				</div>
				<div class="testimonial-div">
					<img src="/static/images/testimonial-img5.jpg"/>
					<div class="testimonial-content">
						<h4>Dr. Manuj Wadwa</h4>
						<h5>Director and Head Max Elite Institute of Orthopaedics and Joint Replacements – Upper North Region, Max Healthcare</h5>
						<p>“In the little over one year I have spent at Max, I have realized what sets this organization apart are the deeply entrenched values in the ethos of system. Max gives you a work environment where your values and virtues get deeply entwined with the professionalism that one desires as a surgeon. Medical wisdom coupled with ultra-modern infrastructure sets the foundation for a progressive work atmosphere. We celebrate ‘evolution’, we celebrate technology and we celebrate the future of Orthopaedics and undoubtedly the futuristic leap in the way medical excellence is witnessed. Like they say, “Who says sky is the limit, when there are footprints on the moon!”</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="testimonial-div">
